Talks are continuing between the General Industries Workers Union of South Africa and Clover. Courtesy of #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - Clover workers marched to the unions’ headquarters as executives from Milco meet with Clover to decide the future of the company. READ: Clover Strike | Clover denounces violent attack The workers want Milco to withdraw and for the government to nationalise Clover. Watch the video above for more details   